title: Meadowview Estates Mobile homes for rent
posting_body: ['3 Bedroom / 2 Bath mobile homes for Rent!!', '  Starting at $735.00.', '  Application fee: $25.00 per person age 18 and older.', '  Pets ALLOWED, breed restrictions apply, limit 2 per home.', ' Office hours:  Monday-Friday 7.30am-3:00PM, Closed for lunch 11.30am-12:00PM.', 'Meadowview Estates  UNDER NEW OWNERSHIP and MANAGEMENT!', '   Must pay security deposit and pay first months rent.', 'Must be able pass back ground check no felonies and Credit check.', 'Must not have any past evictions, or bankruptcy .', ' Please call for additional information 219.762.5312.Please note we are by appointment only due to Covid-19.', 'Please do not email.']
